":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"如果都你求個title ，大陸有得賣phd，功課可以買，試可以代考。<br />\n如果係求知識，讀bussiness嚟做咩，business 緊係落手做喇。"},{"pid":"1071d3e964ef30087643c2d89d6648914a8e6f2c","tid":2273253,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20dcc048ef77d152f2c6171cbab990de78478bbb","tid":2273253,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:52:22.000Z","msg":"讀MBA既目的係咩?做富豪既目的係咩?<br />\n你有錢去名牌大學捐錢起座以自己名命名既學院，然後自己做埋院長都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdea9bf13c33d907d3d319c4f39df5645b3f45a","tid":2273253,"uid":56424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"有EMBA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa24f93a380a2e9da10d4d14cf160501f5325b87","tid":2273253,"uid":380835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dcdea9bf13c33d907d3d319c4f39df5645b3f45a","tid":2273253,"uid":56424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"有EMBA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:49:01.000Z","msg":"讀完 EMBA，可否直升三大PhD拎Research Scholarships?"}]}